com.vividsolutions.jcs.conflate.linearpathmatch.split
Class SplitEdge

java.lang.Object
  com.vividsolutions.jcs.conflate.linearpathmatch.split.SplitEdge
public class SplitEdge
extends java.lang.Object

An edge of a the final geometry of a SplitPath. This edge may correspond to either:

  • a section of an edge that has been split
  • an original edge which has not been split
